Module org.example
Package org.example

Class Connect

java.lang.Object
org.example.Connect
public class Connect
extends java.lang.Object
The Connect class represents connect from database. The new object one is constant. We can create a Connect object like this: Connect connect = new Connect ("195.150.230.210", "5434", "2021_urban_radoslaw", "2021_urban_radoslaw", "33209") or Connect connect = new Connect ("path to file with properties").
